headline: Incyte Gears Up to Report Q1 Earnings: Here's What You Should Know
summary: INCY is likely to beat Q1 earnings estimates, primarily driven by increased U.S. sales and royalties from Novartis on ex-U.S. sales of its lead drug, Jakafi.
